

+ =Matthew 5:28= :: You have heard that it was said, ‘Do not commit adultery.’ But I say to you that anyone who looks at a woman lustfully has already committed adultery with her in his heart.

You can look at a woman lustfully, but you cannot commit adultery with her in your heart.
You have to purge your heart of the desire to commit adultery.
You have to purge your heart of the desire to look
